---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/brand/favicon.svg" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/brand/favicon-32x32.png" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/brand/favicon-16x16.png" />
		<link rel="icon" href="/brand/favicon.ico" sizes="any" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Benchmarks Portal | YangsAI</title>
		<meta
			name="description"
			content="Benchmarks portal for YangsAI. Track benchmark suites, evaluation status, reproducibility notes, and release updates."
		/>
		<style>
			:root {
				--bg-0: #0a0d10;
				--bg-1: #11161c;
				--line: #66727f;
				--text: #e8edf3;
				--muted: #b3bfcb;
				--accent: #d5dde6;
			}

			* {
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			body {
				margin: 0;
				min-height: 100vh;
				font-family: "IBM Plex Sans", "Avenir Next", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
				color: var(--text);
				background:
					radial-gradient(1200px 560px at -8% -6%, rgba(220, 232, 246, 0.14), transparent 52%),
					radial-gradient(900px 460px at 108% 0%, rgba(154, 173, 194, 0.12), transparent 56%),
					linear-gradient(160deg, var(--bg-0), var(--bg-1));
			}

			.frame {
				margin: 0 auto;
				max-width: 980px;
				padding: 3.2rem 1.1rem 2rem;
			}

			.hero {
				border: 1px solid rgba(213, 221, 230, 0.22);
				border-radius: 1.2rem;
				padding: 1.3rem;
				background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(20, 26, 33, 0.72), rgba(15, 20, 25, 0.72));
				box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
			}

			.badge {
				display: inline-block;
				font-size: 0.69rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.14em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: var(--muted);
			}

			h1 {
				margin: 0.6rem 0 0;
				font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.6rem);
				line-height: 0.96;
				letter-spacing: -0.02em;
			}

			.lead {
				margin: 0.95rem 0 0;
				max-width: 64ch;
				color: var(--muted);
				line-height: 1.65;
			}

			.grid {
				margin-top: 1.2rem;
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
				gap: 0.7rem;
			}

			.card {
				border: 1px solid rgba(213, 221, 230, 0.18);
				border-radius: 0.9rem;
				padding: 0.9rem;
				background: rgba(17, 21, 27, 0.58);
			}

			.card h2 {
				margin: 0;
				font-size: 0.92rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.08em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: var(--accent);
			}

			.card p {
				margin: 0.45rem 0 0;
				font-size: 0.92rem;
				color: var(--muted);
			}

			.actions {
				margin-top: 1rem;
				display: flex;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				gap: 0.55rem;
			}

			.btn {
				display: inline-block;
				border-radius: 999px;
				border: 1px solid rgba(213, 221, 230, 0.28);
				padding: 0.46rem 0.9rem;
				color: var(--text);
				text-decoration: none;
				font-size: 0.82rem;
			}

			.btn:hover {
				background: rgba(213, 221, 230, 0.12);
			}

			footer {
				margin-top: 1rem;
				font-size: 0.77rem;
				color: #9aa7b5;
			}

			@media (max-width: 780px) {
				.grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<main class="frame">
			<section class="hero">
				<span class="badge">benchmarks.yangs.ai</span>
				<h1>Benchmark Portal</h1>
				<p class="lead">
					Single-page entry point for YangsAI benchmark programs. This portal is designed for rapid updates,
					reproducibility reporting, and transparent release tracking.
				</p>

				<div class="grid">
					<article class="card">
						<h2>Suites</h2>
						<p>Catalog benchmark suites by modality, data source, and task family.</p>
					</article>
					<article class="card">
						<h2>Status</h2>
						<p>Publish current run status, known issues, and pending validation checks.</p>
					</article>
					<article class="card">
						<h2>Releases</h2>
						<p>Track changelogs, version tags, and migration notes for benchmark users.</p>
					</article>
				</div>

				<div class="actions">
					<a class="btn" href="https://yangs.ai" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Visit Main Site</a>
					<a class="btn" href="mailto:contact@yangs.ai">Contact Team</a>
				</div>
			</section>

			<footer>YangsAI Benchmarks Portal • Built with Astro</footer>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
